<Page x:Class="KurobaChan.Pages.SoftwareAdd.Pge_Welcome"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
      xmlns:local="clr-namespace:KurobaChan.Pages.SoftwareAdd"
      mc:Ignorable="d"
      Height="415" Width="800">
	<Grid>
		<TextBlock x:Name="Tbk_Content" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="20" FontSize="10pt">
			Welcome to KurobaChan Program Add wizard.<LineBreak />
			<LineBreak />
			The wizard will help you to add a new external program to database, which window can be hidden and shown by KurobaChan.<LineBreak />
			<LineBreak />
			If you're ready, click "Next".<LineBreak />
			<LineBreak />
			Note: It is required to start the target program at least once for necessary information to be collected during wizard process.<LineBreak />
			If you want to add a program that is not suitable to start in current environment (e.g. adding NSFW game in work environment), please close this wizard and wait for appropriate time to start again.
		</TextBlock>
	</Grid>
</Page>
